  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>디자인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0757ca03-6029-4d59-9c9c-c30cca2358c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a3cd5f1a-77a1-48ca-94ef-7fb910a0640f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fc378dca-000e-4ed8-9d6b-011df2bfb38f\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>진심</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-412a281c-16c5-421f-b445-37d6cc97384f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">카탈로그의 절반 이상이 무선제본입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>무선제본(Perfect Binding)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57cec74-1276-4799-bc79-31936b65d833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 내용이 많아서 거의 32pages가 넘어갈 때 사용하는 제본 방식입니다. 페이지가 많아지면 중철, 즉, 스테이플러로 찍어서 제본하는데 문제가 생겨 인쇄의 대수별로 접어서 겹쳐 표지를 감싸는 방식으로 제본을 하게 되는데 그것을 우리는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-392725bf-d47a-4521-b6cc-d71163a5fb24\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>무선제본</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-69a0136f-88e7-4e3b-a5e5-c232bf8ce5e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이라고 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bed5750c-9417-45b9-843e-8f47352d0bbf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:472px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a76dec26-582d-44c0-b4c4-bd4cf7b370e1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b192fa96-41af-4171-ba24-bda05917d49d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21e639b7-6559-4ac3-a5bf-37ab24e99e99\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d5e6312-a49b-4dee-90d0-8de848c3584a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05cf0eca-df7a-4a05-8e78-b0ea2b295ceb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 페이지가 적어서 무선제본으로 제작하기 어렵다면 중철 제본으로 제작됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-473bbdc9-7aba-4bd3-b8aa-c0022136e60d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a9cfbfa-333c-492d-81a0-333f6d6ce07e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:557px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ed89246c-4784-460a-b392-faa28b6b217d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-247249ce-5440-4253-9960-5ef5a2b6f0cb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7805fa97-4a07-4312-b099-262401ae61e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">무선과 중철의 차이는 책등의 유무입니다. 무선은 두껍기 때문에 책등이라는 높이가 생깁니다. 하지만 중철 제본은 표지 + 내지를 한 번에 접어서 스테이플러로 찍어 제본을 하기 때문에 책등이 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c2466a08-b100-4c4c-8996-5baf09058d0f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:566px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0609300f-2340-42e1-8ed2-0d7df6d16574\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c7665a4-633c-4f8b-8a96-d4923d76b5bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d542f93-936b-4921-a553-70419458dbca\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">책등 계산기는 여러 군데 사이트에서 쉽게 찾으실 수 있습니다. 못 찾으시면 문의하시면 친절히 안내드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-81322482-77c0-45a2-8697-aff8b9ee043d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8309f8eb-f7fd-415d-8213-1a2ebacf6ace\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ac570a8d-8bdd-4a5f-8c5a-a52a2d627486\" style=\"\">사이즈와 책등 설명</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-201bad87-9f68-49d4-9d25-da87cec46284\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a5990ac-0560-496d-9741-9048a0d1ffc2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-736eb3f6-1026-4b4b-a6b9-f4626846597c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>중철 제본은</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-93e44d23-2731-4e27-a999-3521829bb27f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 책등이 없습니다. 그러므로 표지 앞, 뒷면의 공간이 발생되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-44d1908f-d69e-472e-b5d9-f80067d77e38\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5db52380-7a1a-449a-b431-ab4397732e0a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5820e76-0487-48c8-805f-4bee2ff5c769\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a74c7f4-f2e5-481c-9699-22b5957a232a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">A4 사이즈는 210mm × 297mm입니다. 가로가 210mm이므로 위의 이미지대로 구성됩니다. 하지만 세로가 210mm라면 아래 이미지와 같이 구성됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42b448be-e3e0-4e68-9744-f6f57c676df6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b926eb7-4577-490b-a1b6-a15cd818d889\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f195d63b-d340-4071-bf1c-8c36d759c9b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-149f9b28-c69a-4133-86b5-990fc876d1e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 이미지에서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a63d1f87-9be0-4a68-84b4-0dd922d01008\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">빨간색</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a175e2b0-3882-4054-b208-6fb64ae2b0f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 재단되는 선이고 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a892b55-9dd9-435e-b336-69f12775a1ed\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\">파란색</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05afc27e-961a-4f64-9d82-df8189fadc6f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 작업이 이루어지는 선입니다. 보통 재단선과 편집선의 여백은 2~3mm 정도입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f02f3564-d043-457a-9391-a590e7221347\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c863503c-4409-4987-ac85-57511c8f4858\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cfd4a9f3-9ace-4601-81d0-9b73393c1ef3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-206efa34-b8ed-47e1-ba8c-6a1aae9b68a0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4edc862-8b2c-46b0-8e25-6d689fe16117\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b01b7e5-0690-4dc8-ae1c-d9815daf57dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>무선제본</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3597637b-4110-4997-a7dd-98a2094afb29\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이라면 사이에 책등이 있게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9b1c9576-6987-4986-85b9-d21742d61e11\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da9811c5-e1f3-4ace-8236-53e2c6a6f99a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3c822e5-f2c0-48d1-95db-c330d60a8e8d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-accb7967-8ea1-4f1e-babe-b39da9cd9245\" style=\"color:#555555;\">책등은 센터를 기준으로 오시를 넣어서 접게 되므로 센터를 중앙에 위치시키는 것이 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1343c086-2598-4530-93a3-065cc33152f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ed7f4241-ff7e-41a7-b52c-5d1c25448151\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9f2e29a7-b8a4-4470-ac80-9a010f9a56ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e57bb3c7-45cd-4b8b-a76d-667018cd1526\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">책등이 약간은 움직이거나 종이의 미세한 평량 차이로 오차가 발생할 수 있으므로 이를 감안하여 디자인하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-73989b0a-1574-4fb5-8a22-d4c3fe35df1d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d278bf9-6de8-45f8-9ab3-c0d2651fee8f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-003f6d9f-b289-4288-b04c-6cbc11d7cf5b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-438f45e4-4664-4f3c-b033-f1a1eecb571a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">무선제본의 책등 디자인에서 조금은 유의해야 할 디자인이 간격에 경계를 넣는 디자인입니다. 이렇게 되면 책등의 계산을 정확하게 했을 때 이뻐 보이지만 그렇지 않으면 조금은 삐뚤어져 보일 수 있으니 유념하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-28513a4b-a01e-45ff-be01-d10bc32ec4e1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8fdd4543-6df2-4839-8b8e-67bc9c64c805\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:740px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-75ea0ab4-5020-409b-8cc9-49eea958a642\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b8c192e-07a3-4b3f-b651-6d5a0470de9d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4c4ff457-9037-4cb5-884d-90fbf3863079\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">책등의 접히는 부분이 잘 맞으면 이쁘게 접힐 수 있지만 만약에 조금이라도 삐뚤면 표지 쪽에 넘쳐서 보이게 되니 유념하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b3c69ba9-46d4-4e45-8b5b-8cd299d94a0c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dadd9691-0bcb-49a3-b6d1-ca7e01df3513\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6baa1cc3-58b8-461e-96a5-b3f171d8b66d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd542ebd-8b71-4168-921a-bd0f9c01fa7e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9733cb8-03a5-4073-98db-4a7a461ccc35\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지처럼 약간은 오버 돼서 보이는 것을 볼 수 있습니다. 그러므로 이런 이미지는 가급적 차이가 날 수 있음을 감안하여 유념하는 것이 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9d600b77-632c-4647-8d8c-a89c871e0f00\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ece317cc-e2d9-4c5d-ad56-7dad669c7419\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd5fc4a5-3024-45a8-8beb-25964c9729c9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3b1742a6-5015-4619-b707-6c2a09825171\" style=\"color:#555555;\">책등(세네카)이 안 맞으면 앞, 뒤로 삐져나오게 되어 있습니다. 요즘은 책등 계산이 거의 정확하여 오차가 거의 없지만 그래도 이렇게 정확하게 따지게 되는 디자인은 하지 마시기를 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-42bf1b83-0217-4fa7-996a-bd12d2303ec6\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/013.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/014.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223796900114/015.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b007ff27-f3b3-4092-b7ca-4a04ff22e0f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4cfaa308-c852-47a7-9f05-b369927fb718\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d711f90f-ef97-42ce-81ba-12b6c2c17299\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지들처럼 통일된 색상을 연결하는 것이 무난합니다. 그러면 약간의 오차도 감안하여 보이지 않게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-9faec0f0-bfee-4318-8896-ec058627bf11\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04b00dd1-ab23-4c95-bd5f-823a156803a0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-bc1bc336-d2b7-44fa-a583-f5316d5655ce\" style=\"\">결론</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bd29f8a6-50dc-4f5a-8f02-bf263465d46a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e0e6b117-f978-428d-a573-62024e43cbea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9ac3f41b-422b-45ee-9163-3cdba174a67a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>책등 디자인은 색상을 연결시키는 것이 좋습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70032837-30a2-4245-a3c5-ade041248386\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-35b447a3-73e1-4d81-a6b8-cc44508a5ffa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>책등 계산법은 사이트를 참고하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0cdbc6b3-e4e6-4101-9176-1594e20fdff0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e8190e65-4c06-450a-8bd3-fb387b1d458b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>\"책등 계산기\" 참고 또는 문의하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-488862b6-9ef8-431f-b5aa-2873d9cbb337\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-51807c08-b8b8-4488-8e45-6982c3d5630f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>32p 이상 되는 책자는 무선제본으로 제작하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223796900114#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}